{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "小鱼儿假意要与铁心兰分手，声称男女有别不能再同行，令铁心兰伤心离去。但小鱼儿放心不下，暗中跟踪，发现铁心兰病倒在路旁，高热昏迷。小鱼儿将她抱到海晏镇最好的客栈，亲自煎药照料多日。铁心兰病中醒来，发现小鱼儿为照顾她已数夜未眠，感动落泪。小鱼儿嘴硬心软，一边威胁要打她屁股逼她吃药，一边细心呵护。铁心兰康复后，小鱼儿从靴子中取出之前藏好的一张重要破纸，原来他早已识破铁心兰的谎言。铁心兰感动之下将破纸相赠。此时小仙女张菁率安西镖局和定远镖局的镖师追查至此，小鱼儿用偷来的人皮面具为两人易容扮成老夫妻，从小仙女眼皮底下从容脱身。逃出后小鱼儿故作无情要再次分手，铁心兰伤心欲绝给了他一耳光。小鱼儿正欲离去，一个神秘的冷笑者突然出现。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不……不……唉，不错，兰花的兰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我知道你现在心里很彷徨，也不知要到哪里去，也不知该怎么办，所以，我不说话，让你静静想一想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你究竟有多少岁？……我有时真害怕，不知道你究竟是个真正的孩子，还是个……是个……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "妖怪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我有时真忍不住要以为你是精灵变幻而成的，否则，你为什么总是能猜中别人心里的事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "因为我比世上所有的人都聪明得多。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "也许你真的是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "好，现在你想通了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "想通什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你可想通你究竟该怎么办？到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你可要快些想，我不能总是陪着你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你不能？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "自然不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但……但本来……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不错，本来我想和你结伴，到处去闯闯，但现在你既然是个女人，我计划就要变了，我也不能再要你做徒弟了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你……你……你……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我和你非亲非故，两个人在一起到处跑算什么？何况，我还是有许多事要做，怎么能被个女人缠着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，我和你非亲非故，你……你走吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "那么你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我自然有我去的地方，用不着你关心。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "好，你现在只怕还不能走路，这匹马，就送给你吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "谢谢，但……但我也用不着你的马，我什么都用不着你的，你……你……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你用不着也好，我本也有些舍不得这匹马，我若和它分别，倒真还有些难受。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "好，我走了，但愿你多多保重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我自然会保重的，我用不着你假情假意地来关照我，我……我但愿死也不要再见你！",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小白菜，你瞧我可是个聪明人，这么容易就将个女人打发走了，你要知道，女人可不是好打发的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小白菜，你猜她会到哪里去，你猜不着吧？……告诉你，我也猜不着，咱们在这里等等，偷偷瞧瞧好么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能瞧瞧女孩子的秘密，总不是件坏事，何况……咱们也没有什么事急着去做，等等也没关系，是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走……小白菜，咱们再瞧瞧去，瞧瞧她究竟要搞什么鬼？你要知道，我可不是关心她，我是什么人都不关心的。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "喂，这里可不是睡觉的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "走！走！谁要你回来的，你回来干什么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你病了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我病了也用不着你管，你……你和我非亲非故，你为什么要管我？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我现在就偏偏又要管你了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我不要你碰我。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我偏要碰你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你敢碰我……你放手，你滚。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你已病得要死了，再不乖乖的听话，我……我就又要脱下你的裤子打屁股了，你信不信？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你为什么……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不准开口。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不准哭，吃药，这是最好的药方，最好的药，你吃下去后，立刻就会好了，若像小孩子似的好哭，就又要打屁股了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这……这是谁开的药方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "原来你还会看病，你难道什么都会？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不准开口，吃药。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不准我开口，我怎么吃药呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江小鱼呀江小鱼，你切莫忘记，女孩子这样对你笑的时候，就是想害你，就是想弄条绳子套住你的头，她对你越温柔，你就越危险，只要一个不小心，你这一生就算完了。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小白菜，你放心，别人纵会上当，但我却不会上当的，等她病一好，我立刻就走……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_mian_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "麻面大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "镖银入安西，太平送到底……安西镖局的大镖师岂不是从来不丢东西的么，怎地连自己耳朵都丢了，这倒是奇案。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_ba_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "刀疤大汉",
      "listener": "char_ma_mian_da_han",
      "text": "若是被人打肿了脸，还是莫要笑的好，笑起来疼得很的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_mian_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "麻面大汉",
      "listener": "char_dao_ba_da_han",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_ba_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "刀疤大汉",
      "listener": "char_ma_mian_da_han",
      "text": "大哥莫说二哥，大家都是差不多。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳老者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "安西镖局和定远镖局，平日虽然难免互相争生意，抢买卖，但那也不过只是生意买卖而已，大家究竟还都是从中原来的江湖兄弟，千万不可真的动起手来，伤了兄弟间的和气。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "徐老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳大哥说的不错，咱们这些人被总局派到这种穷地方来，已是倒了楣了，大家都是失意人，又何必再呕这种气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳老者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何况，咱们今日这筋斗，还像是栽在同一人的手上，大家本该同仇敌忾才是，怎么能窝里反，却让别人笑话。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "徐老大",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_lao_zhe",
      "text": "各位莫非也是被她……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳老者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是她是谁？除了她，还有谁会莫名其妙地下如此毒手，唉！咱们弟兄今天可真算栽了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_mian_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "麻面大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若真是为着什么，咱们被那丫头欺负，那倒也罢了，只恨什么事也不为，那丫头就出手了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳老者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖之中，本是弱肉强食，不是我长他人志气，咱们武功实在连人家十成中的一成都赶不上，纵然受气，也只得认了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "徐老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但瞧那丫头的模样，也像是在别处受了欺负，非但眼睛红红的，像是痛哭了一场，就连她那匹宝贝马都不见了，只怪咱们倒楣，恰巧撞在她火头上，她就将一肚子气都出在咱们身上了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_mian_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "麻面大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "徐老大说得不错，那丫头想必是遇上了比她更厉害的，也说不定遇着个漂亮的小伙子，非但人被骗去了，就连马也被人骗走了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "张菁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫你们去找人，谁叫你们来喝酒！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "那双破靴子，叫化子穿都嫌太破，你可惜什么？紧张什么？我已替你买了双新的，比那双好十倍！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你扔到哪里？快带我去找！你……你这死人，你可知道我那靴子，靴子里藏着……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "藏着什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "就是那东西……我为了它几乎将命都送了，但你却将它扔到阴沟里，我……我不如死了算了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "那东西？那东西不是不在你身上么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那是我骗你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "谁要你骗我，这一来你可是自己害自己，我把那破靴子随手一扔，根本不知道扔在哪里了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好……很好……什么都完了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "那东西也只不过是张破纸而已，丢了也没什么了不起，你又何苦如此着急，急坏了身子可不是好玩的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你怎知道那……那是张纸？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你若说的就是那张纸，我已从靴子里拿出来过，纸不但已破了，还是臭臭的，有股臭咸鱼的味道。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这死人……你故意让我着急。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "谁叫你骗我……我早已猜出那东西是在你靴子里的……你居然想得出把那么重要的东西藏在靴子里，可真是个鬼灵精。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你才是鬼灵精，什么事都瞒不过你，你……你方才真骇死我了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "但东西还是落在我的手里，你不着急？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "在你手里，我还着急什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你不怕我不还给你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我不怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "好，我就不还你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那，我就送给你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "但……但你本来死也不肯将这东西给别人的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你和别人不同。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "方才你到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "外面……我还瞧见了一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这人你认得的……我不幸也认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小……小仙女？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "对了，就是她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "她在哪里？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你打开窗子只怕就可见到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "她……她就在外面，你却还有心在这里和我开玩笑？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "她就在我面前，我也是照样开玩笑。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这人……现在，我们该怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "现在，三十六着，走为上策，咱们……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好啦，走也走不了啦！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "看样子小仙女已找了人一间间屋子查过来了，她想必已听说咱们落脚在这附近，但现在他们还未查到这里，咱们赶紧从窗子逃出去，还来得及。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不行，咱们现在若从窗里逃走，他们就必会猜出咱们了，那时小仙女追踪而来，咱们也是逃不远的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那……那怎么办？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不怕，我自有法子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这女人莫非正在洗澡。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这是宝贝……是我从一个姓屠的人那里偷来的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这莫非就是人皮面具？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "总算你还识货。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你先脱下外面的衣服，随便塞在哪里……再把我这斗篷，反着披在身上……好，现在把脸伸过来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "真像是活见鬼，你……你竟已变成个小老头了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "小老头正好配小老太婆。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "莫怕……莫怕，我这易容改扮的功夫，虽还并不十分到家，但唬唬他们已足够有余了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "走，咱们从大门出去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "大……大门！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大爷们让让路，我这老婆子也不知吃错了什么，突然得了重病，再不快去瞧大夫，就要送终了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_mian_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "麻面大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "六月天突然发病，八成是打摆子，否则怎会冷得发抖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马儿马儿，老太婆虽病了，我可也不能丢下你。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "老天，求求你，走快些好么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "千万不能走快，他们或许还在后面瞧，走快就露相了……你瞧夜色这么美，骑在马上慢慢逛，多么富有诗情画意。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这人……我真猜不出你的心究竟是什么做的？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "心？……我这人什么都有，就是没有心。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "方才那把刀若是砍下，你就连头也没有了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我早就知她那把刀只不过是试试我的，她若真瞧破了我，真要动手，又怎会再去拔别人的刀？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错……你在那种时候居然还能想到这种关节，你真是个怪人……你难道从来不知道害怕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你以为我不害怕？……老实告诉你，我也怕得要死，世上只有疯子白痴才会完全不害怕的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "咱们现在到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "到哪里去都没关系了，反正再也没有人能认得出你……只是，你的病……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我方才被他们一骇，骇出一身冷汗，病倒像是好了，手脚也像是有了力气，你说怪不怪？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你已能走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "能，不信我下马走给你看看。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "好，你下马走吧……我也要走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你……你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我们不是早已分手了么？只因为你有病，我才照顾你，现在你病好了，我们自然还是各走各的路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你难道真的……真的……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "自然是真的，你将那东西送给了我，我也救了你一命，咱们可算两相抵过，谁也不欠谁了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你难道真的没有心……你……你的心莫非已被狗吃了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这次你猜对了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "幸好我的心已被狗吃了，我真该谢谢那条狗，否则男人的心若被女人捏在手里，倒真不如被狗吃了算了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不是人……你根本不是人！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "再见吧……无论我是不是人。至少不是能被女人眼泪打动的呆子，我……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_xiao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "冷笑者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，你不是呆子，你聪明得很！只可惜太聪明了些！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    }
